                Protect What Matters.<br/>
                <span class="text-blue-400">Insure Your Journey.</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                Experience peace of mind with our 24/7 claim assistance and instant digital policy generation. Join 10,000+ vehicle owners today.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
                <a href="#quick-start" class="px-10 py-5 bg-blue-600 text-white font-black rounded-2xl shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-3">
                    Get Instant Quote <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
                </a>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl border border-white/20">
                    <div class="flex -space-x-3">
                        <img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-900" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=1" alt="User">
                        <img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-900" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=2" alt="User">
                        <img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-900" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=3" alt="User">
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white tracking-tight">4.9/5 Rating</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

